de.bioforscher.singa.structure.parser.pdb.structures.tokens

Interface PDBToken

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AtomToken, ChainTerminatorToken, HeaderToken, ModelToken, TitleToken

    public interface PDBToken
    Tokens are used to extract information from PDB lines. Each token is identified by a static record pattern. Afterwards the information from the line can be extracted.
